
=Bio=

[[Liquid Feedback]] Developer. Board Member of [[Public Software Group Association]]. Board Member of [[Association for Interactive Democracy]]. LiquidFeedback is an independent open source project published under MIT license by the [[Public Software Group]] of Berlin, Germany. The developers of LiquidFeedback have teamed up in the Association for Interactive Democracy to support the use of electronic media for democratic processes.

